---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Band-Kostenrechner"
  description="Kalkuliere die Kosten für deine Hochzeitsband oder Partyband. Konfiguriere deine Band maßgeschneidert für deine Veranstaltung."
>

  <Hero
    title="Band-Kostenrechner"
    subtitle="Kalkuliere die Kosten für deine Band und konfiguriere sie maßgeschneidert für deine Veranstaltung."
    backgroundImage="/images/wp/2024-02-DZ.074.6397-scaled.webp"
  />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:860px;">

      <p class="intro-text">
        Ob Hochzeitsfeier, Geburtstagsparty oder Sommerfest: Kalkuliere präzise die Kosten
        für deine Hochzeits- oder Partyband und konfiguriere deine Band maßgeschneidert
        für deine Veranstaltung!
      </p>
      <p class="intro-text-sub">
        Außerdem kannst du unverbindlich unsere Verfügbarkeit an deinem Wunschtermin checken.
      </p>

      <!-- Info-Banner -->
      <div class="info-banner">
        <div class="info-banner-icon">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="info-banner-text">
          <p>Dieser Kostenrechner gilt für <strong>private Events</strong> wie Hochzeiten, Geburtstage, Jubiläen und private Feiern. Die Kalkulation bezieht sich auf unsere <strong>fünfköpfige Standardbesetzung</strong> (Sängerin, Sänger, Keys, Gitarre, Drums).</p>
          <p style="margin-top:0.4rem;">Bei <strong>Firmenevents</strong> und öffentlichen Veranstaltungen erstellen wir euch gerne ein individuelles Angebot – <a href="/booking/">schreibt uns einfach</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="calc-wrapper">

        <!-- Step 1: Datum -->
        <div class="calc-step">
          <div class="step-header">
            <span class="step-number">1</span>
            <h3>Wann findet euer Event statt?</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="datepicker-wrap">
            <button type="button" class="datepicker-trigger" id="datepickerTrigger">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
              <span id="datepickerLabel">Datum wählen</span>
            </button>
            <div class="datepicker-dropdown" id="datepickerDropdown">
              <div class="dp-header">
                <button type="button" class="dp-nav" id="dpPrev">
                  <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"/></svg>
                </button>
                <span class="dp-month-year" id="dpMonthYear"></span>
                <button type="button" class="dp-nav" id="dpNext">
                  <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
                </button>
              </div>
              <div class="dp-weekdays">
                <span>Mo</span><span>Di</span><span>Mi</span><span>Do</span><span>Fr</span><span>Sa</span><span>So</span>
              </div>
              <div class="dp-days" id="dpDays"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2: Musikstile -->
        <div class="calc-step">
          <div class="step-header">
            <span class="step-number">2</span>
            <h3>Welche Musikstile wünscht ihr euch?</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="step-hint">Mehrfachauswahl möglich. Pro Stil könnt ihr die Anzahl der Sets (je 45 Min.) wählen.</p>

          <div class="style-grid">
            <!-- Party -->
            <div class="style-card" data-style="party">
              <button type="button" class="style-toggle" data-style-btn="party">
                <div class="style-icon">
                  <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M9 18V5l12-2v13"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="16" r="3"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="style-name">Party</span>
                <span class="style-price">950 € / Set</span>
              </button>
              <div class="set-selector" data-sets="party">
                <label>Anzahl Sets:</label>
                <div class="set-counter">
                  <button type="button" class="counter-btn" data-action="decrease" data-target="party">−</button>
                  <span class="counter-value" data-count="party">1</span>
                  <button type="button" class="counter-btn" data-action="increase" data-target="party">+</button>
                </div>
                <span class="set-duration" data-duration="party">45 Min.</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Standardtanz -->
            <div class="style-card" data-style="standardtanz">
              <button type="button" class="style-toggle" data-style-btn="standardtanz">
                <div class="style-icon">
                  <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="4" r="2"/><path d="M15 22V13.5l2.5-4.5L15 7H9L6.5 9l2.5 4.5V22"/><path d="M9 13l-3 9"/><path d="M15 13l3 9"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="style-name">Standardtanz</span>
                <span class="style-price">700 € / Set</span>
              </button>
              <div class="set-selector" data-sets="standardtanz">
                <label>Anzahl Sets:</label>
                <div class="set-counter">
                  <button type="button" class="counter-btn" data-action="decrease" data-target="standardtanz">−</button>
                  <span class="counter-value" data-count="standardtanz">1</span>
                  <button type="button" class="counter-btn" data-action="increase" data-target="standardtanz">+</button>
                </div>
                <span class="set-duration" data-duration="standardtanz">45 Min.</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Dinner / Lounge -->
            <div class="style-card" data-style="dinner">
              <button type="button" class="style-toggle" data-style-btn="dinner">
                <div class="style-icon">
                  <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 010 8h-1"/><path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 01-4 4H6a4 4 0 01-4-4V8z"/><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"/><line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"/><line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="style-name">Dinner / Lounge</span>
                <span class="style-price">500 € / Set</span>
              </button>
              <div class="set-selector" data-sets="dinner">
                <label>Anzahl Sets:</label>
                <div class="set-counter">
                  <button type="button" class="counter-btn" data-action="decrease" data-target="dinner">−</button>
                  <span class="counter-value" data-count="dinner">1</span>
                  <button type="button" class="counter-btn" data-action="increase" data-target="dinner">+</button>
                </div>
                <span class="set-duration" data-duration="dinner">45 Min.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3: Add-ons -->
        <div class="calc-step">
          <div class="step-header">
            <span class="step-number">3</span>
            <h3>Zusätzliche Leistungen</h3>
          </div>

          <div class="addon-grid">
            <label class="addon-card" data-addon="trauung">
              <input type="checkbox" id="addonTrauung" />
              <div class="addon-content">
                <div class="addon-icon">
                  <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.78z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <span class="addon-name">Begleitung Trauungsfeier</span>
                  <span class="addon-desc">Musikalische Begleitung eurer Trauung</span>
                </div>
                <span class="addon-price">+ 400 €</span>
              </div>
            </label>

            <label class="addon-card" data-addon="dj">
              <input type="checkbox" id="addonDJ" />
              <div class="addon-content">
                <div class="addon-icon">
                  <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="22"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <span class="addon-name">DJ-Service</span>
                  <span class="addon-desc">Professioneller DJ vor, zwischen und nach den Live-Sets</span>
                </div>
                <span class="addon-price">+ 750 €</span>
              </div>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Kalkulation -->
        <div class="calc-result" id="calcResult" style="display:none;">
          <h3>Eure Kalkulation</h3>
          <div class="result-table-wrap">
            <table class="result-table">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th>Leistung</th>
                  <th class="col-qty">Sets</th>
                  <th class="col-price">Preis</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody id="resultBody"></tbody>
              <tfoot id="resultFoot"></tfoot>
            </table>
          </div>

          <p class="result-hint">Alle Preise verstehen sich zzgl. Anfahrt. Die Kalkulation dient als Orientierung – euer individuelles Angebot erstellen wir nach eurer Anfrage.</p>

          <!-- CTA: Verfügbarkeit prüfen -->
          <div class="cta-section">
            <div class="cta-glow"></div>
            <h3 class="cta-title">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
              Prüfe unsere Verfügbarkeit
            </h3>
            <p class="cta-subtitle">Sichert euch euren Wunschtermin – unverbindlich und kostenlos.</p>

            <div id="inquirySuccess" class="inquiry-success" style="display:none;">
              <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
              <h4>Anfrage erfolgreich gesendet!</h4>
              <p>Vielen Dank für euer Interesse. Wir prüfen die Verfügbarkeit und melden uns innerhalb von 24 Stunden bei euch.</p>
            </div>

            <form class="inquiry-form" id="inquiryForm">
              <div class="inquiry-row">
                <div class="inquiry-field">
                  <label for="inquiryName">Name *</label>
                  <input type="text" id="inquiryName" name="name" required placeholder="Euer Name" />
                </div>
                <div class="inquiry-field">
                  <label for="inquiryEmail">E-Mail *</label>
                  <input type="email" id="inquiryEmail" name="email" required placeholder="email@beispiel.de" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="inquiry-field">
                <label for="inquiryPhone">Telefon <span class="optional">(optional)</span></label>
                <input type="tel" id="inquiryPhone" name="phone" placeholder="Eure Telefonnummer" />
              </div>
              <div class="inquiry-field">
                <label for="inquiryMessage">Nachricht <span class="optional">(optional)</span></label>
                <textarea id="inquiryMessage" name="message" rows="3" placeholder="Erzählt uns kurz von eurem Event..."></textarea>
              </div>

              <!-- Hidden fields for calculation data -->
              <input type="hidden" id="hiddenDate" name="wunschtermin" />
              <input type="hidden" id="hiddenCalc" name="kalkulation" />

              <div class="inquiry-field">
                <label class="privacy-label">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="privacy" required />
                  <span>Ich habe die <a href="/datenschutz/">Datenschutzerklärung</a> gelesen und stimme der Verarbeitung meiner Daten zu. *</span>
                </label>
              </div>

              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-large inquiry-submit" id="inquirySubmit">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
                Jetzt unverbindlich Verfügbarkeit prüfen
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Intro Text */
  .intro-text {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto 0.5rem;
  }
  .intro-text-sub {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
  }

  /* Info Banner */
  .info-banner {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.25);
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .info-banner-icon {
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .info-banner-text p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .info-banner-text strong {
    color: #ddd;
  }

  /* Calculator Wrapper */
  .calc-wrapper {
    background: var(--color-surface-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    padding: 2.5rem;
  }

  /* Steps */
  .calc-step {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .calc-step:last-of-type {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .step-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .step-header h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .step-number {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .step-hint {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: calc(32px + 0.85rem);
  }

  /* Datepicker (reused from booking) */
  .datepicker-wrap {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 320px;
    margin-left: calc(32px + 0.85rem);
  }
  .datepicker-trigger {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .datepicker-trigger:hover { border-color: var(--color-primary); }
  .datepicker-trigger.has-value { color: #e0e0e0; }

  .datepicker-dropdown {
    display: none;
    position: absolute;
    top: calc(100% + 0.5rem);
    left: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    border: 1px solid #333;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 1rem;
    width: 300px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }
  .datepicker-dropdown.open { display: block; }
  .dp-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .dp-month-year { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #fff; }
  .dp-nav {
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    color: #999;
    cursor: pointer;
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
  }
  .dp-nav:hover { background: #333; color: var(--color-primary-light); }
  .dp-weekdays {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .dp-weekdays span {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #666;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    padding: 0.25rem 0;
  }
  .dp-days {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
  }

  /* Style Cards */
  .style-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    padding-left: calc(32px + 0.85rem);
  }
  .style-card {
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .style-toggle {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
    color: var(--color-muted);
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
  }
  .style-toggle:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: #e0e0e0;
  }
  .style-card.active .style-toggle {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.12);
    color: #fff;
  }
  .style-icon {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.1);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
  }
  .style-card.active .style-icon {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: #fff;
  }
  .style-name {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .style-price {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  /* Set Selector */
  .set-selector {
    display: none;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.2);
    border-top: none;
    border-radius: 0 0 var(--radius-card) var(--radius-card);
    margin-top: -14px;
    padding-top: calc(0.85rem + 14px);
  }
  .style-card.active .set-selector {
    display: flex;
  }
  .style-card.active .style-toggle {
    border-radius: var(--radius-card) var(--radius-card) 0 0;
  }
  .set-selector label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .set-counter {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .counter-btn {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: background 0.15s;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }
  .counter-btn:hover { background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.15); }
  .counter-value {
    width: 32px;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }
  .set-duration {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-left: auto;
  }

  /* Add-ons */
  .addon-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding-left: calc(32px + 0.85rem);
  }
  .addon-card {
    cursor: pointer;
    display: block;
  }
  .addon-card input {
    position: absolute;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .addon-content {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
  }
  .addon-content:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  .addon-card input:checked + .addon-content {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.1);
  }
  .addon-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.1);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .addon-card input:checked + .addon-content .addon-icon {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: #fff;
  }
  .addon-name {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #e0e0e0;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }
  .addon-desc {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin-top: 0.15rem;
  }
  .addon-price {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-primary-light);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* Result */
  .calc-result {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 2.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    animation: fadeSlideIn 0.4s ease-out;
  }
  @keyframes fadeSlideIn {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  .calc-result h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .result-table-wrap {
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
  .result-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
  }
  .result-table th {
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
